enumber\">11\u003C/span>[ος πά]ντας οἵτινες ἐντάδε ἀφικνοίατο μεˉδέν’ \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Εὐνίκοˉ\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Εὐνίκοˉ\">Εὐνίκοˉ\u003C/span>\u003C/span> σπευδαιό-\u003Cbr id=\"al12-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">12\u003C/span>[τερο]ν γενέσθαι, μέˉτ’ ἄνδρεσι μέˉτε γυναικέσσι ὁς οὗτος &lt;ὁ&gt; βόλιμοˉς τὸˉς τε\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">.\u003C/span>-\u003Cbr id=\"al13-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">13\u003C/span>[νον? επ]ο̣&lt;ι&gt;δ{ι}α̣ὶ̣ τιμὰν ἐρύσαιντο \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Εὐνίκοˉι\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Εὐνίκοˉι\">Εὐνίκοˉι\u003C/span>\u003C/span> ἀὲ νίκᾶν παντε῀ ἐμ βολύμοι̣ ἐπ̣-\u003Cbr id=\"al14-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">14\u003C/span>[ὶ φιλ]ότατι τᾶι \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Εὐνίκοˉ\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Εὐνίκοˉ\">Εὐνίκοˉ\u003C/span>\u003C/span> γάρφοˉ \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.14 reg., orig. άρ\u003C/p>",{"author":3,"date":4,"citedRange":115,"ptr":116,"ref":118,"inscriptionDate":4,"title":2,"citation":5,"uri":6,"year":4},"138-140",{"target":117},"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/D6NXVVJX",{"_":119,"target":119},"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002302",2017,false],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
